{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/SourceProtocol"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setDisposeFunction","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"dispose","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"GSourceDisposeFunc","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@GSourceDisposeFunc"},{"kind":"text","text":"?)"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"code":"dispose","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" function will be called once the reference count of ","type":"text"},{"code":"source","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"reaches zero but before any of the state of the source is freed, especially"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"before the finalize function (set as part of the [type","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/SourceFuncs","type":"reference"},{"text":"]) is","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"called.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This means that at this point ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"source"},{"type":"text","text":" is still a valid [struct"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Source"},{"type":"text","text":"]"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"and it is allow for the reference count to increase again until ","type":"text"},{"code":"dispose","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"returns.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The dispose function can be used to clear any ‘weak’ references to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"source"},{"type":"text","text":" in other data structures in a thread-safe way where it is"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"possible for another thread to increase the reference count of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"source"},{"text":" again","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"while it is being freed."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The finalize function can not be used for this purpose as at that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"point "},{"code":"source","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is already partially freed and not valid any more.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This should only ever be called from [struct","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Source"},{"type":"text","text":"] implementations."}]}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/SourceProtocol\/setDisposeFunction(dispose:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Method","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setDisposeFunction","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"dispose","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"GSourceDisposeFunc","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@GSourceDisposeFunc"},{"text":"?)","kind":"text"}],"externalID":"s:4GLib14SourceProtocolPAAE18setDisposeFunction7disposeyySpySo8_GSourceVGSgXCSg_tF","extendedModule":"GLib","title":"setDisposeFunction(dispose:)","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"GLib"}],"symbolKind":"method"},"abstract":[{"text":"Set ","type":"text"},{"code":"dispose","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" as dispose function on ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"source"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLangu